ygData.messageBody:
I actualy know a way to get the Executioner's Hood without going to
Lguk...Do the gnasher quest (bring the note to the guy in surefall and bring
another note to the captain at the ground of fait) then when the exicutioner
takes the prisioner to be exicuted you can kill him for the hood and axe.

Trevalien
